        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Airline Freeze of Astronomical Increases in Rates Act or the AirFAIR Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes it an unfair or deceptive practice to impose an excessive price increase for air transportation tickets in circumstances related to a disaster or emergency.</p> The Department of Transportation must issue regulations to establish standards for determining whether an increase in a ticket price is considered excessive.]]></text>
      </summary>
